                  Tests.Cases
                  Tests.Properties
                  Tests.Strictness
                  Tests.TH

   Other-Extensions: CPP
                     EmptyDataDecls
                     FlexibleContexts
                     FlexibleInstances
                     FunctionalDependencies
                     MultiParamTypeClasses
                     NoMonomorphismRestriction
                     PatternGuards
                     TemplateHaskell
